[SN]TITLE[SN]
BBC Sports Personality of the Year: #spotyselfies

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
We asked you to send in your star-studded selfies as we look forward to the BBC Sports Personality of the Year show in Glasgow on Sunday night.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
You didn't disappoint with a gallery of top-class performers.
And you can still send in snaps via twitter at #spotyselfie with the best being shown in our live event coverage.
BBC Sport online coverage kicks off at 17:00 GMT before a red carpet show on the red button from 18:15, 5 live from 19:30 and the big BBC1 show from 20:00.
